Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.18,1:05:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.16,1:05:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.85,1:05:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,yonder hill
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.21,1:05:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望我可在那边的山上
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.61,1:05:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,'Tis there I'd sit
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.81,1:05:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and cry my fill
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.03,1:05:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我就能坐在那里流尽泪水
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.43,1:05:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,'Til every tear would
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.12,1:05:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,turn a mill
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.67,1:05:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,直至泪水可以让磨坊转动
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.98,1:05:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is go dté
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.92,1:05:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,tú mo mhúirnín
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.34,1:05:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,slán
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.25,1:06:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,愿你能平安归来，我的爱人
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.90,1:06:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,上文出自爱尔兰语传统歌谣Siúil A Rún（来吧，我的爱人）
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.58,1:06:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这摇曳的森林
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.32,1:06:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是风的记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.72,1:06:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,散落的果实
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.07,1:06:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,被带到了这里
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.90,1:06:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,行路的人啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.61,1:06:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,发现了什么呢
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.03,1:06:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,星星会满足
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.10,1:06:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那个愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.76,1:07:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.07,1:07:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,如何是好
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.16,1:07:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有终结的话
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.83,1:07:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.32,1:07:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,如此便好
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.96,1:07:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,若能归为一处
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.81,1:07:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,追求着无形的某种事物
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.63,1:08:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,彷徨直至今日
